org.digitalertachograph.DDDQuery.internalData.DataTypes
Class CertificateRequestID

java.lang.Object
  org.digitalertachograph.DDDQuery.internalData.DataClass
      org.digitalertachograph.DDDQuery.internalData.DataTypes.CertificateRequestID

public class CertificateRequestID
extends DataClass

Unique identification of a certificate request. It can also be used as a Vehicle Unit Public Key Identifier if the serial number of the vehicle unit to which the key is intended is not know at certificate generation time.
